        "timestamp": "2018-03-09 14:43:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n\"One more thing\" ... all of the Python-facing Music API and related code (including messaging and so on) was to be factored out into its own project (python-music). I had begun this a while back but was then moved off Music before it could be finished. I would strongly recommend this work be resumed at some point. I have the beginnings of it and would be happy to share and/or contribute to its completion in my infinite spare time. Ping me! :)",
